%% Diagram: Edit-commit state machine for inline cell editing
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ViewMode: focus cell
    ViewMode --> EditMode: F2 / Enter / dblclick / printable key
    ViewMode --> ViewMode: arrow keys move focus

    state EditMode {
        [*] --> Dirty: keystroke
        Dirty --> Validating: blur / Tab / Enter
        Validating --> Pending: valid + onCellEditRequest
        Validating --> Dirty: invalid (show error)
        Pending --> Committed: server ack / sync write
        Pending --> Reverted: server reject
    }

    EditMode --> ViewMode: Escape (cancel, restore original)
    Committed --> ViewMode: focus moves (Enter ↓, Tab →)
    Reverted --> ViewMode: toast + revert
